name: Dr. Dyle Xenoblade Fan Version
description:
Some space-time disturbance has ocurred on Dyle's Island and two new Fan levels appeared (look for the clouds and the cliffs!))

This game doesn't accept donations but you can see our other games!

All Xenoblade characters are property of Nintendo and Monolith Soft, and are included in this game with pure fun purposes as fanart.

Xenoblade music remixes are also owned by Nintendo, Monolith Soft and ACE, and were remixed by Tate-Tot Tunes (go follow in youtube!).
